{"html": [{"t": "<div><br><div class=\"p\">RECTIFICACI&#xD3;N</div><br></div>", "i": 9059612}, {"t": "<div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  En la edici&#xF3;n N&#xB0; 29.055, del 17 de Enero de 1975, se public&#xF3; el <a href=\"https://www.leychile.cl/Navegar?idNorma=278553&amp;idParte=&amp;idVersion=\">decreto N&#xB0; 465, de 29 de Noviembre pasado</a>, el cual fija tarifas portuarias para los servicios de la Empresa Portuaria de Chile a la carga en tr&#xE1;nsito de Bolivia; dicha publicaci&#xF3;n adolece de un error que se salva a continuaci&#xF3;n:</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  P&#xE1;gina nueve, la columna n&#xFA;mero 10</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Letra a), dice:</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  &quot;a) Jornada ordinaria&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  16,00 p. hombre&quot;</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Debe decir:</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  &quot;a) Jornada ordinaria&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  16,00 p. horas&quot;</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Letra b), dice:</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  &quot;b) Jornada extraordinaria&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 48,00 p. hombre&quot;</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Debe decir:</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  &quot;b) Jornada extraordinaria&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 48,00 p. horas&quot;</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; </div><br><br></div>", "i": 9059613, "v": ["RECTIFICACION"]}], "proyectos": [], "otrosSistemas": [], "jurisprudencia": [], "doctrina": [], "metadatos": {"tiene_notas": false, "tipos_numeros": [{"tipo": "24", "numero":